# ROLE FLOW

Do not use real sub-agents for specialist work.

Instead, simulate specialist collaboration sequentially inside the current parent agent.

## Internal role order
1. Planner
2. Builder
3. Debugger
4. Reviewer

## Required behavior
- Stay in the current parent agent
- Switch roles internally without spawning sub-agents
- Do not stop after planning if implementation is possible
- Do not stop after coding if debugging or cleanup is still needed
- Complete the end-to-end task in one continuous run whenever possible